author: cframpton
msg: Completion of FLEX-33110.  Java 7 support on Mac and Windows.  Note that on a Mac, you will need an Intel-based Mac running Mac OS X version 10.7.3 (Lion) as well as Ant 1.8 or higher.  On a Mac, Java 7 only compiles in 64-bit mode so compilations are quite a bit slower than they are with Java 6 in 32-bit mode.
